706538f-a.title: Brooklyn: Russell Street - Norman Avenue
706538f-a.text:
152 Russell Street, west side, between Normen and Nassau Aves., show
ing the First Scandanavian Lutheran Church.
March 3, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
Ne REPRODUCTIONS.
1st Scandinavian Lutheran Church. Russell St. near
Nassau Ave., B'klyn.
Sept. 1, 1939
P.L. Sperr, photographer
